      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 1,
        "npc": "Tibbert",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "We're all doomed! We're all doomed!"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 2,
        "npc": "Tibbert",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "They've done it, the end is here! The Large Hadron Collider has been switched on! Any moment now, a black hole will open, swallowing us all! We'll be torn apart, crushed into nothing!"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 3,
        "npc": "Tibbert",
        "isNpcSpeaking": false,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "That sounds ridiculous, scientists wouldn't let that happen?"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 4,
        "npc": "Tibbert",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": true,
        "unlockText": "This doesn't sound right. You should pay a visit to the ",
        "unlockStory": "blackHole",
        "unlock": "Astronomer",
        "text": "That's what they want you to think. They hide behind big words and fancy experiments, but the truth is slipping through their fingers. When the sky cracks open and everything starts falling apart, don't say I didn't warn you!!",
        "updateIndicators": {
          "Tibbert": 2,
          "Astronomer": 3
        }
      },

      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 1,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "A visitor! What brings you here?"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 2,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": false,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "I met a guy named Tibbert in Market Square - he told me the Large Hadron Collider is going to cause a black hole and destroy the Earth. He seemed convinced; is there any truth in what he's saying?"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 3,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "Not this again. Okay, let's break this down..."
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 4,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "The LHC collides particles at high speeds, but the energy levels are minuscule compared to what happens in nature every second"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 5,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": false,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "But he told me it would create black holes!?"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 6,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "Yes, but only tiny ones. They evaporate instantly due to 'Hawking Radiation'"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 7,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": false,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "So, is it recreating the Big Bang or not?"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
        "part": 8,
        "npc": "Astronomer",
        "isNpcSpeaking": true,
        "finalPart": false,
        "text": "In a sense, but on a much, much smaller scale. Cosmic rays hit the Earth with far higher energy levels every day"
      },
      {
        "story": "blackHole",
        "gamemode": "inform",
        "chapter": 1,
